<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; background-color: #ffdce0; text-align: center; font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; overflow: hidden; height: 100vh; }
        
        .flower { position: absolute; font-size: 24px; animation: fall linear infinite; }
        @keyframes fall { to { transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(360deg); } }

        .card { 
            position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0);
            background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            transition: transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            width: 80%; max-width: 400px;
        }
        .card.show { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); }
        
        h1 { color: #eb4d4b; margin-top: 0; }
        p { font-size: 1.1em; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; text-align: justify; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div id="flower-container"></div>

    <div class="card" id="myCard">
        <h1>Happy Birthday!</h1>
        <p>happy birthday to you you have given me the best days and weeks of my life i apologize if i almost forgot it i just wanna say even tho sometimes you have all the problems in life and family i am here for you and my wish for you is i want you to smile more like how you make me smile everyday just one message on you i will smile in overjoy i understand how hard working you are your creative and a beautiful sunshine brightening in my eyes, your perfect and i want you to know that i know in always saying that
        but im just telling the truth im like your mother im here for your comfort and here to cheer your feelings up from being down to up, ilysm and i hope your healthy and staying smiling.
        <br><br>
        HAPPII BIRTHDAYYYYYY MY LOML ပျော်ရွှင်စရာ မွေးနေ့လေး ဖြစ်ပါစေဗျ။</p>
    </div>

    <script>
        function createFlower() {
            const f = document.createElement('div');
            f.innerHTML = '🌸';
            f.className = 'flower';
            f.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + 'vw';
            f.style.animationDuration = Math.random() * 3 + 2 + 's';
            document.getElementById('flower-container').appendChild(f);
            setTimeout(() => f.remove(), 5000);
        }
        setInterval(createFlower, 300);

        setTimeout(() => {
            document.getElementById('myCard').classList.add('show');
        }, 3000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
